				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Wonderful upcoming changes...<a name="13262"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 15 03 10:17 AM</span></td>
